====================================
= pieOS - Android for your PC.
====================================

PieOS aims to provide an Android boot experience with a modular system architecture.

Current status:
- Early development
- GRUB currently used as a bootstrap layer
- Kernel and initrd integration in progress

Goals:
- Fast startup
- Minimal visible boot stages
- Seamless transition from boot to the system environment

==========================================================================================================
WARNING!
THE PROJECT IS STILL UNDER DEVELOPMENT AND HAS BEEN MARKED BY OUR TEAM AS NOT BOOTABLE. DO NOT USE IT.
==========================================================================================================
